                  "description": "Only applicable for Key Type 'External Certificate'. Enter your PEM-encoded X.509 certificate (e.g -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----MIIHyDCCBrCgAwIB[...]CAq8Tn7kSFDmVnrXe6v8hcQ==-----END CERTIFICATE-----)",
